 "bbox": [144.8, 1257.5, 156.4, 1279.0]}, {"text": "In 2012, we recorded restructuring and other charges of $150 million ($176 million after-tax or $0.11 per share) related to", "bbox": [179.7, 1257.5, 1141.8, 1279.0]}, {"text": "the transaction with Tingyi.", "bbox": [179.7, 1280.8, 397.7, 1302.3]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [144.8, 1309.9, 156.4, 1331.3]}, {"text": "In 2012, we recorded a pension lump sum settlement charge of $195 million ($131 million after-tax or $0.08 per share).", "bbox": [179.7, 1309.9, 1112.6, 1331.3]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [144.8, 1339.0, 156.4, 1360.4]}, {"text": "In 2012, we recognized a non-cash tax benefit of $217 million ($0.14 per share) associated with a favorable tax court decision", "bbox": [179.7, 1339.0, 1141.8, 1360.4]}, {"text": "related to the classification of financial instruments.", "bbox": [179.7, 1362.2, 591.4, 1383.7]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [144.8, 1391.3, 156.4, 1412.8]}, {"text": "In 2011, we incurred merger and integration charges of $329 million ($271 million after-tax or $0.17 per share) related to our", "bbox": [179.7, 1391.3, 1141.8, 1412.8]}, {"text": "acquisitions of PBG, PAS and WBD.", "bbox": [179.7, 1414.6, 476.3, 1436.0]}]}